
This is version 2.1.9 of the Perl Package Manager, PPM.

See the POD contained in bin/ppm.pl for information on how to use the
PPM client.

See the POD contained in lib/PPM.pm for information on how to use the
PPM library to write an alternative client.

Any patches (particularly documentation and setup) that make it a
more generally useful tool will be gratefully accepted.

Murray Nesbitt <murray@cpan.org>

